Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:13.00,0:36:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.08,0:36:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.05,0:37:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:28.01,0:37:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗?  好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:32.01,0:37:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较喜欢吃甜的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.02,0:37:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜的很喜欢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:43.09,0:37:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体看不出来有胖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.04,0:37:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.04,0:38:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.04,0:38:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人听到我讲话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:03.11,0:38:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有过发胖吗?没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:07.12,0:38:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.12,0:38:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动呢?   没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.05,0:38:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没注意过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.06,0:38:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃着喜欢的西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.06,0:38:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想睡就睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.07,0:38:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肆意的生活对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.07,0:38:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动   不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:30.07,0:38:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.01,0:38:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:36.08,0:38:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:40.08,0:38:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.02,0:38:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗? 有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.09,0:38:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几乎很少压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.03,0:38:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.03,0:39:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡了以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:01.04,0:39:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.04,0:39:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.11,0:39:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会因为减肥烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.05,0:39:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都蛮开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.12,0:39:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不需要减肥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.12,0:39:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吃什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:24.13,0:39:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.13,0:39:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃饭也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.00,0:39:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.00,0:39:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃零食就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:35.07,0:39:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还不胖阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.01,0:39:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几岁了   24
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.01,0:39:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.08,0:39:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.01,0:39:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.08,0:39:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们好好看你的身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.09,0:39:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要激烈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.09,0:40:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:02.03,0:40:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有激烈了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.03,0:40:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.04,0:40:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要更色的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.11,0:40:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很M很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:18.05,0:40:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:20.05,0:40:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看过其他人影片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.12,0:40:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.05,0:40:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.06,0:40:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.13,0:40:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好冰
